  "subject": "Make git commit linter less strict",
  "commit_message": "Make git commit linter less strict\n\n- make line length restrictions for the git commit linter less strict [0]\n\n[1] oom changes fail all the time, because lines in the commit message are too long.\nThis encourages short, but meaningless commit messages.\n\nIssue-ID: OOM-3304\nChange-Id: I364037f9c2fcbd4ad1f2e8c8788a08c73e83376b\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <Fiete.Ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
